bug_reported_acknowledgement:
Thank you for reporting a bug in Launchpad. Launchpad is open source software. If you want to you can help fix the bug you are reporting. See <https://dev.launchpad.net/> for more information.

We will triage your bug soon: we need to make sure we can reproduce it as well as determining where it fits in the project's priorities.
bug_reporting_guidelines:
This is the Launchpad bug queue. Please include the exact URL of a page where you had the problem, along with information on how to reproduce it. If the bug you found generated an OOPS id, please include it here as well.

Also see https://dev.launchpad.net/BugHandling

If you're reporting a bug about Ubuntu, you're in the wrong place. Try <https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu>.
description: Launchpad is a unique collaboration and hosting platform for software projects. It is being built by a team at Canonical in South Africa, Scotland, and Canada, where we are using it in our own projects. We want to turn it into the best place to collaborate on free software, by building tools to make such collaboration easier and more effective. See /canonical for our commercial offering.
